'''Emyn Muil''' is a Italian epic black metal solo project<ref>https://www.metal-archives.com/bands/Emyn_Muil/3540358234</ref> created by Nartum, that makes music related to Tolkien. Nartum created it in 2012 and has released three CD albums. It is named after the [[Emyn Muil]].
